BusinessName.BusinessNameLine1Txt: ST MARY'S HOME FOR THE AGED INC

IRS990.ActivityOrMissionDesc: TO CONTINUE THE HEALING MINISTRY OF JESUS WITH PARTICULAR ATTENTION TO THE NEEDS OF THE POOR, AS WE PROVIDE SKILLED NURSING CARE AND HOUSING FOR SENIORS.
IRS990.MissionDesc: AS A FACILITY THAT PROVIDES SKILLED NURSING, REHABILITATION, ASSISTED LIVING, AND INDEPENDENT LIVING, ST. MARY'S CONTINUES THE HEALING MINISTRY OF JESUS BY PROVIDING COMPASSIONATE CARE THAT SUPPORTS THE VALUES OF RESPECT FOR HUMAN DIGNITY, COMPASSION, TRANSFORMATION, SOLIDARITY WITH THE POOR AND JUSTICE AND PEACE.
IRS990.Desc: ST. MARY'S EMPLOYS OVER 300 PEOPLE IN DIRECT CARE AND SUPPORT RESPONSIBILITIES, REPRESENTING APPROXIMATELY 80,000 RESIDENT DAYS PER YEAR. CARE IS PROVIDED IN SKILLED NURSING, ASSISTED LIVING AND INDEPENDENT LIVING. SIGNIFICANT COMMUNITY SERVICE IS PROVIDED BY BOTH INDIVIDUALS SERVING ON BOARDS AND COMMITTEES AND BY THE ORGANIZATION SERVING AS A CLINICAL SITE FOR CURRICULUM REQUIREMENTS AND TRAINING FOR REGIONAL POST-SECONDARY EDUCATIONAL INSTITUTIONS IN ADDITION TO HOSTING VARIOUS OTHER EDUCATIONAL PROGRAMS.DURING 2022 - 2023, ST. MARY'S HOME PROVIDED IN EXCESS OF $900 THOUSAND IN UNREIMBURSED SERVICES FOR MEDICAID, FAMILY CARE, MEDICARE, AND MANAGED CARE RESIDENTS. IN ADDITION, HUNDREDS OF HOURS WERE DONATED TO AREA AGENCIES IN SUPPORT OF COMMUNITY ORGANIZATIONS AND EVENTS THAT BENEFIT RESIDENTS OF MANITOWOC COUNTY AND THE SURROUNDING AREAS. AMONG THE ORGANIZATIONS SUPPORTED THROUGH STAFF INVOLVEMENT ARE: ROTARY MANITOWOC, LAKESHORE TECHNICAL COLLEGE, FIRST PRESBYTERIAN CHURCH, ALZHEIMER'S ASSOCIATION, CHAMBER OF MANITOWOC COUNTY, MANITOWOC COUNTY YOUTH APPRENTICE PROGRAM, LEADING AGE- WISCONSIN, MANITOWOC COUNTY LEADERSHIP COMMITTEE, NATIONAL ASSOCIATION OF CATHOLIC CHAPLAINS, PETER'S PANTRY, HOMELESS HYGIENE DRIVE RECIPIENTS (HOPE HOUSE, INCOURAGE DOMESTIC VIOLENCE SHELTER, LAKESHORE CAP SUPPORTIVE HOUSING PROGRAM, LUTHERAN SOCIAL SERVICES RUNAWAY & YOUTH SERVICES, PAINTING PATHWAYS CLUBHOUSE, SOUTHFIELD NEIGHBORHOOD NETWORK LEARNING CENTER, TEE-BOX TRANSITIONAL SOBER LIVING, THE HAVEN OF MANITOWOC COUNTY, THE CROSSING) THE SALVATION ARMY, AND MANITOWOC COUNTY HISTORICAL SOCIETY. ST. MARY'S SERVED AS A CLINICAL SITE FOR LP AND AD NURSING STUDENTS ATTENDING LAKESHORE TECHNICAL COLLEGE, AND ONE CLINICAL PASTORAL EDUCATION CHAPLAIN STUDENT.FINALLY, ESTIMATED COSTS TO PROVIDE ALL THE ABOVE OPPORTUNITIES IS $23,054.

SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE ORGANIZATION HOLDS CASH ON BEHALF OF CERTAIN RESIDENTS IN A SEPARATE CHECKING ACCOUNT, WHICH IS USED TO PAY FOR THE RESIDENTS' INCIDENTAL EXPENSES.

THE HOME ESTABLISHED THE ST. MARY'S HOME ENDOWMENT FUND AS A PERMANENTLY RESTRICTED PERPETUAL ENDOWMENT FUND TO PROVIDE SUPPORT TO THE CHARITABLE MISSIONS OF ST. MARY'S AT FELICIAN VILLAGE, THE COURT AT FELICIAN VILLAGE, THE VILLA AT FELICIAN VILLAGE, AND THE GARDENS AT FELICIAN VILLAGE. THE ENDOWMENT CONSISTS OF INVESTMENTS ESTABLISHED TO FUND ITS MISSIONS AND IS DONOR-RESTRICTED. AS REQUIRED BY GENERALLY ACCEPTED ACCOUNTING PRINCIPLES, NET ASSETS ASSOCIATED WITH ENDOWMENT FUNDS, INCLUDING FUNDS DESIGNATED BY THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS TO FUNCTION AS ENDOWMENTS, ARE CLASSIFIED AND REPORTED BASED ON THE EXISTENCE OR ABSENCE OF DONOR-IMPOSED RESTRICTIONS.

ST. MARY'S HOME FOR THE AGED, INC., IS A NOT FOR PROFIT ORGANIZATION UNDER SECTION 501(C)(3) OF THE INTERNAL REVENUE CODE AND IS EXEMPT FROM INCOME TAXES ON RELATED INCOME UNDER SECTION 501(A) OF THE CODE. THE HOME FOLLOWS THE ACCOUNTING STANDARDS FOR UNCERTAINTY IN INCOME TAXES. THESE STANDARDS REQUIRE ENTITIES TO DISCLOSE IN THEIR FINANCIAL STATEMENTS THE NATURE OF ANY UNCERTAINTIES IN THEIR TAX POSITION. AREAS THAT THE INTERNAL REVENUE SERVICE AND STATE TAX AUTHORITIES CONSIDER WHEN EXAMINING TAX AND INFORMATION RETURNS OF A TAX-EXEMPT ENTITY INCLUDE, BUT ARE NOT LIMITED TO, TAX-EXEMPT STATUS AND THE EXISTENCE AND AMOUNT OF UNRELATED BUSINESS INCOME. THE HOME DOES NOT BELIEVE THAT IT HAS ANY UNCERTAIN TAX POSITIONS WITH RESPECT TO THESE OR OTHER MATTERS, AND HAS NOT RECORDED ANY UNRECOGNIZED TAX BENEFITS OR LIABILITY FOR PENALTIES OR INTEREST.
